title: Greens Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, Bakery, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Licensed cafe and bistro offering some vegetarian dishes that can also be made vegan and are marked. Sample menu items such as 3-bean chilli with rice, jacket potato, or tortilla chips, vegan option shepherds pie, daily vegan soup, sandwich and other jacket potato fillings. Food is made on the premises.
